'&lt;a href="http://www.llanellirailwaystrikeriots.info/"&gt;Remembrance of a Riot: the story of the Llanelli Railway Strike Riots of 1911&lt;/a&gt;' by John Edwards&lt;br /&gt;
'&lt;a href="http://www.manifestopress.org.uk/index.php?option=com_content&amp;amp;view=article&amp;amp;id=24:killing-no-murder-communist-review-summer-2010&amp;amp;catid=7:reviews&amp;amp;Itemid=6"&gt;Killing No Murder – South Wales and the Great Railway Strike of 1911&lt;/a&gt;' by Robert Griffiths&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5343320711385594995-921976148100775271?l=www.radicalwales.org' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
